  "prompt": "How do I apply winter internship in Rourkela Steel Plant?",
  "response": "To apply for a winter internship at Rourkela Steel Plant (RSP), you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Check Eligibility\n- Be a student of Engineering/Diploma/Degree\n- Recommended disciplines: Metallurgy, Mechanical, Electrical, Computer Science, etc.\n\n2. Visit Official Website\n- Go to www.sail.co.in (SAIL official website)\n- Check \"Careers\" or \"Internship\" section\n\n3. Application Methods\n- Online application through SAIL website\n- Direct email to HR Department\n- Contact RSP's HR office directly\n\n4. Prepare Documents\n- Updated resume\n- College ID proof\n- Academic transcripts\n- Recommendation letter from college\n\n5. Contact Details\n- Rourkela Steel Plant HR Department\n- Phone: (0661) 2660111\n- Email: recruitment.rsp@sail.in\n\n6. Additional Recommendations\n- Check RSP website regularly\n- Follow SAIL's official social media channels\n- Network with alumni working in RSP\n- Attend campus placement drives\n\n7. Application Timeline\n- Typically, applications open between August-October\n- Internship duration: Usually 4-8 weeks during winter\n\nNote: Specific details might vary, so direct communication with RSP is recommended.",
